    <h3>Getting Started</h3>
    <p>This demo allows you to interact with the Learnosity Grading API. Follow these steps:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>Configure your Learnosity credentials in the Configuration panel</li>
        <li>Click "Update Configuration" to initialize the grading interface</li>
        <li>Use the "Attach Items" panel to add specific items for grading</li>
        <li>Grade the items using the provided interface</li>
        <li>Click "Submit Grading" to save your work</li>
    </ol>
    
    <h3>Troubleshooting</h3>
    <p>If you encounter any issues:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Check that your API credentials are correct</li>
        <li>Ensure the item references are valid</li>
        <li>Check the browser console for detailed error messages</li>
    </ul>
